<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> نفسه ص ٢٠ وما بعدها.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> لسان العرب <span class="c2">((نصص)</span>) .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> تاج العروس <span class="c2">((نصص)</span>) ، وانظر إشكاليّة التحيّز ص ٢٧٥.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
